Weekly 154
Question is there are houses given . their positions in an x array
we have to set up a grocery store such that sum of absolute differences of grocery store and all the houses is minimum
Recall that such a point is median !!! # DAI yad kro 


int minimumDis(int n, vector<int> x) {
        sort(x.begin(),x.end());
        return x[(n-1)/2];
    }
